## 9.10 Risk Mitigation

| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|-------------|--------|------------|
| Client data doesn't match CSV format | High | High | Provide sample CSVs, validation with clear errors |
| Performance degrades with large fleet | Medium | High | Limit demo to 200 trains, virtualize train list |
| deck.gl/Konva integration issues | Medium | Medium | Have fallback all-Konva implementation ready |
| Zoom transitions feel jarring | Medium | Medium | Add CSS transitions between renderers |
| Projection algorithm has edge cases | Low | High | Comprehensive test suite, manual override mode |

